    <title>Hexo tutorial</title>
    <url>/2021/03/17/HexoTutorial/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="writing-organizing-content">Writing &amp; Organizing Content</h2>
<ul>
<li>創新md檔案至 ~/Documents/Hexo/你的資料夾名稱/source/_posts <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p>創草稿md檔案至 ~/Documents/Hexo/你的資料夾名稱/source/_drafts <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new draft b</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure> <span id="more"></span></p></li>
<li><p>在瀏覽器預覽draft檔案 <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server --draft </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></li>
<li><p>發表draft檔案，檔案也會從 ~/_draft 被移到 ~/_posts <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo publish b </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></li>
<li><p>在 ~/Documents/Hexo/你的資料夾名稱/_config.yml中<bt> <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">default_layout: post</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure> 改成 <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">default_layout: draft</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure> 如此一來用 <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure> 就會預設創建草稿 (這才對吧，哪有人一new就發文ㄉ==)</p></li>
<li><p>除了draft跟post以外，可以創單一個page<br> 這檔案會被存在 <個人網址>/aboutme <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new page aboutme</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="scaffolds">Scaffolds</h2>
<ul>
<li>Scaffolds裡面放了三個檔案用來定義Front Matter (創建md檔時的前幾行)<br>
<ul>
<li>draft.md</li>
<li>page.md</li>
<li>post.md</li>
</ul>
所以說可以透過修改這些檔案讓default format有更多花樣~</li>
</ul>
<p>以修改 ~/scaffolds/draft.md 為例 <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: &#123;&#123; title &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure> 可以改成 <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: &#123;&#123; title &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">author: Yuan</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">## H1 TEXT</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="tags-categories">Tags &amp; Categories</h2>
<p>在Front Matter新增 <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">tags: [tag1, tag2, tag3]</span><br><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line">- [cat1, cat1.1]</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure> 如果tags跟categories的頁面沒出現就自己新增 <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new page tags</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo new page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure> 接著修改<br> 1. source/tags/index.md <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: tags</span><br><span class="line">date: 產生當下時間</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line">comments: false</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure> 2. source/categories/index.md <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: categories</span><br><span class="line">date: 產生當下時間</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">comments: false</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="tag-plugins">Tag Plugins</h2>
<p>可以用Plugins放codeblock或是iframe (youtube)之類的<br> 1. 插入程式碼 <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% codeblock lang:python%&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    code...</span><br><span class="line">    code...</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endcodeblock %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure> <figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">add</span>(<span class="params">x, y</span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> x+y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure> 2. 插入youtube <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% youtube I07XMi7MHd4%&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure> <div class="video-container"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/I07XMi7MHd4" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></p>
]]></content>
