    <title>json筆記</title>
    <url>/2021/03/19/json%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>因為在設定hexo時必須修改一堆.yml檔，而剛好yml跟json很像，所以就做了這篇簡短的筆記。</p>
<h2 id="簡介">簡介</h2>
<p>json (JavaScript Object Notation)，唸法同<strong>Jason</strong>，跟yaml一樣都是key-value寫法。<br> 差別在:<br> <span id="more"></span></p>
<ul>
<li>換行的時候json要加逗號而yaml不用</li>
<li>json的key要加雙引號</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="寫法">寫法</h2>
<figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123; </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;person&quot;</span>:&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;name&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;Yuan&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;age&quot;</span>: <span class="number">26</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;gpa&quot;</span>: <span class="number">3.2</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;fav_num&quot;</span>: <span class="number">1e+10</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;male&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">true</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;flaws&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">null</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hobbies&quot;</span>: [<span class="string">&quot;guitar&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;movies, &quot;</span>coding<span class="string">&quot;],</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    &quot;</span>friends<span class="string">&quot;: [</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">      &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &quot;</span>name<span class="string">&quot;: &quot;</span>Anger<span class="string">&quot;,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &quot;</span>age<span class="string">&quot;: 25</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">      &#125;,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">      &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &quot;</span>name<span class="string">&quot;: &quot;</span>NaYue<span class="string">&quot;,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &quot;</span>age<span class="string">&quot;: 24</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">      &#125;,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    ],</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>可用縮排把上述資料包進person這object裡面
<ul>
<li>呼叫方式: person.gpa</li>
</ul></li>
<li>[]裡面可以存:
<ul>
<li>單變數像hobbies: [xx, xx, xx]</li>
<li>多變數像friends: [{xx, xx}, {xx, xx}]</li>
</ul></li>
<li>記得要逗號~</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="參考來源">參考來源</h2>
<div class="video-container"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gIxLDYvfGcQ" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>
]]></content>
