    <title>yaml筆記</title>
    <url>/2021/03/19/yaml%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>因為在設定hexo時必須修改一堆.yml檔，想說來了解一下它所以就做了這篇簡短的筆記。</p>
<h2 id="簡介">簡介</h2>
<p>yaml簡寫yml唸作<strong>耶某</strong>，很像json很好懂。<br> 副檔名: .yaml or .yml <span id="more"></span></p>
<h2 id="寫法">寫法</h2>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 這是註解</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">person:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">&quot;Yuan&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">occupation:</span> <span class="string">&quot;Incoming Yahooer&quot;</span>  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">age:</span> <span class="type">!!float</span> <span class="number">26</span> <span class="comment"># 26.0</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">birthday:</span> <span class="number">1994-09-22 15:00:00</span> <span class="comment"># ISO 8601</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">gpa:</span> <span class="type">!!str</span> <span class="number">3.2</span> <span class="comment"># &quot;3.2&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">favriate number:</span> <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">male:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">flaws:</span> <span class="literal">null</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">hobbies:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&quot;guitar&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&quot;coding&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&quot;statistics&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">fruits:</span> [<span class="string">&quot;mango&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;apple&quot;</span>]</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">friends:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">&quot;Anger&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">age:</span> <span class="number">25</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> &#123;<span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">&quot;Book&quot;</span>, <span class="attr">age:</span> <span class="number">25</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">&quot;NaYue&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">age:</span> <span class="number">24</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">decription:</span> <span class="string">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">Study</span> <span class="string">in</span> <span class="string">Tokyo</span> <span class="string">now.</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">Recently</span> <span class="string">built</span> <span class="string">a</span> <span class="string">blog</span> <span class="string">with</span> <span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">and</span> <span class="string">gitpage</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">like</span> <span class="string">what</span> <span class="string">you</span> <span class="string">see</span> <span class="string">here.</span> </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">signature:</span> <span class="string">|</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">Yuan</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">Waseda</span> <span class="string">University</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">email:</span> <span class="string">howlen0319@gmail.com</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>可用縮排把上述資料包進person這object裡面
<ul>
<li>呼叫方式: person.gpa</li>
</ul></li>
<li>!!可以強制轉型</li>
<li>hobbies的寫法跟fruits互通</li>
<li>friends下的三種寫法互通，都會被存成list</li>
<li>decription後面的&gt;，可以讓分段的文字被存成一行(分行之類的format不會被保存)</li>
<li>相反的，signature後面的|可以讓format被保存下來</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="進階寫法">進階寫法</h2>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">person:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">&amp;name_var</span> <span class="string">&quot;Yuan&quot;</span> <span class="comment">#&amp;後面的字不一定要跟key一樣</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">id:</span> <span class="meta">*name</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">base:</span> <span class="meta">&amp;base</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">var1:</span> <span class="string">value1</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">foo:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">foo_var1:</span> <span class="string">*base</span> <span class="comment"># var1: value1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>id透過*可以存取name_var也就是&quot;Yuan&quot;</li>
<li>*也可以存取整個key-value pair
<ul>
<li>例如foo的寫法</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
